name: limited edition red kendama holders
description:
Our kendama holders have string and a clip that can clip
Onto belt loops, pants,and many other things. 
The clip has a random color and the string is red. Our kendama holders are great for carrying your kendama. The string has a decorative knot on it that is great for tightening and loosening your holder. KENDAMA NOT INCLUDED.
